_______________________________________________________________________________
"Obscure"         
        This allows the psionicist to mentally obscure his image in
        others' minds.  It is not complete invisibility, it simply
        changes the psionicist's description to "something
        in the corner of your eye" for a short time.  They may know
	someone's there but they won't know who it is unless your own
 	description gives it away.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  9	Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  obscure
